commit af1bd422d127ea968d708952ff49a6c3bb0f44a5
Author: Bruce Guenter <bruce@untroubled.org>
Date:   Mon Apr 15 08:46:52 2013 -0600

    sendmail: Document the -b[mps] mode options in the man page

 doc/sendmail.1 | 16 +++++++++++++---
